    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-q-a/production-order-child-item-is-another-bom-s-parent-item-sap-business-one/qaq-p/13879587</id>
    <title>Production Order Child Item is another BoM's Parent Item SAP Business One</title>
    <updated>2024-09-27T07:33:55.097000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>nikunjmehta2290</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/2002</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Dear all,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Need to understand on BoM Calculation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;If We used One Child item into Production Order which is already Parent Item of another BoM then Child item quantity is not deducted from stock.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;U&gt;Example &lt;/U&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Parent 1&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Child 1&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Child 2&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Here, Child 1 is contain BoM like&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Child 1&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Child 3&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Child 4&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Here, While generate the production order for Parent 1 Item then Child 3 and Child 3 stock is not deducted from Warehouse.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Regards,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Nikunj Mehta&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-q-a/production-order-child-item-is-another-bom-s-parent-item-sap-business-one/qaq-p/13879587"/>
    <published>2024-09-27T07:33:55.097000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
